    <item>
      <title>耶伦称中国副总理的黑客行为引发“严重担忧”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yellen-tells-china-s-vice-premier-hacks-raise-serious-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国表示受中国政府支持的黑客入侵美国财政部计算机网络一周后，美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦向中国国务院副总理何立峰表达了她对“恶意网络活动”的“严重关切”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yellen-tells-china-s-vice-premier-hacks-raise-serious-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 04:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普施压阻止司法部特别检察官报告的发布</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-presses-to-block-release-of-doj-special-counsel-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份新的法庭文件显示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普反对公布司法部特别顾问杰克·史密斯的最终报告，他的律师称该报告指控特朗普“参与了前所未有的犯罪活动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-presses-to-block-release-of-doj-special-counsel-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 04:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾在争议海域与中国“怪物”船对峙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/philippines-confronts-china-s-monster-ship-in-disputed-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着北京方面加大在有争议的南海的活动力度，菲律宾指责一艘被其称为“怪物”的中国巨型海警船在其专属经济区内“非法存在”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/philippines-confronts-china-s-monster-ship-in-disputed-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 03:46:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回国前，布林肯重申与日本的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/blinken-reaffirms-ties-with-japan-ahead-of-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫前两周，国务卿安东尼·布林肯高度评价美国与日本之间密切的经济和安全伙伴关系。]]></description>
